WEBVTT

00:02.450 --> 00:04.113
Previously
on "Criminal Minds"...

00:04.279 --> 00:06.490
Look, a while back I had some
medical issues, headaches,

00:06.590 --> 00:08.529
and there was a geneticist
that I reached out to.

00:08.729 --> 00:10.412
I guess I just-- I think
it's funny how we've been doing

00:10.414 --> 00:13.265
this for 6 months
and we've never met.

00:13.267 --> 00:14.883
Do you think he knows
about us?

00:14.885 --> 00:16.268
As far as I can tell,
he doesn't.

00:16.270 --> 00:18.654
Well, I guess I'll talk
to you next Sunday.

00:18.656 --> 00:20.689
Bye. Love you.

00:20.691 --> 00:24.693
Well, if you've got somebody
new in your life to talk to,

00:24.695 --> 00:26.495
I'd just like to know
who she is.

00:26.497 --> 00:28.897
'Cause she's gotta be one hell
of a woman to keep up with you.

00:28.899 --> 00:30.666
I think the stalker's gone.

00:30.668 --> 00:32.167
The emails have stopped.

00:32.168 --> 00:34.086
What about the phone calls?
No, I haven't gotten any.

00:34.088 --> 00:36.755
No more heavy breathing
on the machine. No more hangups.

00:36.757 --> 00:39.074
Is this about
phone booth girl?

00:39.076 --> 00:40.592
She wants to meet.

00:40.594 --> 00:42.044
Wait,
you guys have never met?

00:42.046 --> 00:43.912
Aren't you curious
what she looks like?

00:43.914 --> 00:46.382
No, it doesn't matter
what she looks like. I mean,

00:46.384 --> 00:49.751
she's already the most beautiful girl
in the world to me.

